---
title: Thai-Style Tofu 'Pad Krapow' with Green Beans
description: Pad krapow is a popular dish in the Thai street food scene. In our version, tofu is stir-fried with aromatic ingredients such as ginger, garlic, lime and chili pepper, then served over fluffy rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pad-krapow-au-tofu-facon-thaie-321424f9.jpg
